<tr><td><strong>KPV</strong></td><td>NF-&kappa;B pathway</td><td>Direct NF-&kappa;B inhibition; reduces IL-1&beta;, IL-6, TNF-&alpha; production; nuclear accumulation</td><td class="y">Moderate (preclinical)</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Thymosin &alpha;1</strong></td><td>T cell regulation</td><td>Enhances Treg function; balances Th1/Th2 response; promotes dendritic cell maturation</td><td class="g">Strong (clinical trials)</td></tr>
